list.name: Default
list.comment: Dialog system: Page switching Locations: Save on area enter, not on client leave (it's unreliable) Disease system: Only display message when infection is actually removed. Inventory system: Decrease the number of system items by 1. Feats: Add CustomFeat enumeration, remove hard coded reference to reload feat. Hunger system: Double the delay between hunger loss cycles.
